videos.description: Miami's Ja'Quan Newton uses a nice spin move to get to the rack and finishes the reverse layup.
videos.headline: Newton gets the reverse layup

videos.description: After a scramble for the ball and a behind-the-back pass, Drew Buggs drills the three to give the Rainbow Warriors the lead against Miami.
videos.headline: Hawai'I takes lead with Buggs three

videos.description: Bruce Bowen Jr. finds Anthony Lawrence II who finishes the lay-in through contact.
videos.headline: Miami gets and-1 on the fast break

videos.description: Anthony Lawrence II blows by his defender and punishes the rim.
videos.headline: Miami's Lawrence throws it down

videos.description: Sheriff Drammeh gives the lead back to the Rainbow Warriors with an off-balance layup plus the foul.
videos.headline: Drammeh gets tough and-1 for Hawai'i

videos.description: Sheriff Drammeh nails a long shot to tie the game at 33-33 going in to halftime with No. 6 Miami.
videos.headline: Hawai'i's Drammeh hits big shot to tie game at half

videos.description: Bruce Brown Jr. uses his court vision to find Lonnie Walker IV who lays it in as the Hurricanes extend their lead.
videos.headline: Miami gets out on the fast break again
